snippet.title: Let's Play Evil Islands - 01
snippet.description: This is my very first LP ever. I decided to try it out on Evil Islands. Please feel free to leave any questions, comments, concerns. Also let me know how the sound is. I know the game sound might be a bit loud at points and overtake my voice, I tired to fix it in the next video.
